{"tid":2182132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港光復紀念日 Liberation Day","createTime":"2020-08-31T06:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T08:58:13.000Z","uid":123774,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"317cc46186fa126c9efed6b9c5dcd50db0608111","tid":2182132,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T06:13:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>香港重光紀念日</strong><br />\n紀念1945年8月30日結束三年零八個月<br />\n為香港犧牲嘅英國+香港士兵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QF4M1C5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQF4M1C5.png&h=28bf0a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日中環和平紀念碑都係紀念二戰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ufz9eZb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfz9eZb.jpg&h=8726abbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主權移交之後 取消咗重光假期<br />\n用支那5.1 10.1去取代<br />\n<br />\n儀式於上午11時在西灣國殤紀念墳場內的紀念碑位置舉行。<span class=\"red\"><strong>英國、加拿大、澳洲、馬來西亞駐港澳總領事館及多國總商會等均派代表出席儀式</strong></span>，以及致送虞美人花環，悼念二戰死難者。由於今年儀式遇上疫情橫流，有別於過往自由入場，大會設約100個名額，觀禮人士需持門票方可內進。而入場前，大會亦已安排人手為入場者測量體溫，又事先在地上貼上標示，讓觀禮者保持社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n港共無人做任何野<br />\n因為香港3年8個月英政府及港人歷史<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>支那當時未出現</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f43887c8ccabe7a3c62b084f71efcf446c9206c","tid":2182132,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"今次支那01 寫得幾詳盡<br />\n太長唔cap過黎 可以去睇下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【二戰結束75年】前華籍英兵自發紀念重光日：我真係好鍾意香港</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/517346/%E4%BA%8C%E6%88%B0%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F75%E5%B9%B4-%E5%89%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%B1%8D%E8%8B%B1%E5%85%B5%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BC%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E6%97%A5-%E6%88%91%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E9%8D%BE%E6%84%8F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C%2F517346%2F%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259D%259F75%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%25B1%258D%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%2585%25B5%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E9%258D%25BE%25E6%2584%258F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0xphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=8bb133a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/517346/%E4%BA%8C%E6%88%B0%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F75%E5%B9%B4-%E5%89%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%B1%8D%E8%8B%B1%E5%85%B5%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BC%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E6%97%A5-%E6%88%91%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E9%8D%BE%E6%84%8F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF</a>"},{"pid":"48ccd4a6a8d8afbb55d101f53694a958823c66b0","tid":2182132,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T06:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864ceb21b33261fe31f8458c6425031a08962f79","tid":2182132,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T06:30:30.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國成立<strong><span class=\"red\">70周年</span></strong><br />\n我哋悼念緊第<span class=\"red\"><strong>75個</strong></span>香港重光記念日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f4ff4949b63f01b62c5107f1eb8ad47c2f4857","tid":2182132,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c